Titolo: Asphalt 8: Airborne

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Asphalt 8: Airborne is a 2013 racing video game, developed by ExoticBikes and Gameloft Barcelona and published by Gameloft as part of the Asphalt series. It was released on August 22, 2013 for iOS and Android, November 13 for Windows 8 and Windows Phone 8, January 15, 2014 for BlackBerry 10,  and April 5, 2015 for Tizen. The game's successor Asphalt 9: Legends was announced on February 26, 2018. The game has about 470 million players, according to the game description in the App Store.

